{"tid":791391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【其身不正】發起「#MeToo」女星涉性侵 溫斯坦律師：極度偽善","createTime":"2018-08-23T18:03:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T01:41:51.000Z","uid":22675,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1516ffd3227a9a40964a65c30f702aae2b9662f3","tid":791391,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T18:03:37.000Z","msg":"17,659<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0823 11:30<br />\n 「#MeToo運動」發起人之一Asia Argento，本身亦捲性侵醜聞。(美聯社)<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n「#MeToo運動」發起人之一Asia Argento，本身亦捲性侵醜聞。(美聯社)<br />\n揭發性侵「#MeToo運動」的發起人之一、意大利女星Asia Argento，近日竟被踢爆曾性侵當年只有17歲的童星Jimmy Bennett。對此，被Argento及多名女星指控性侵的前荷李活製片溫斯坦（Harvey Weinstein）辯護律師布拉夫曼（Benjamin Brafman）狠批，整起事件「偽善的程度令人震驚」。<br />\n<br />\n去年10月，Argento指控哈維韋斯坦，在1997年向當時只有21歲的她性侵得逞。隨後幾個月，「#MeToo運動」如火如荼地演變，這時Argento竟被爆，因性侵22歲男星Bennett正向對方和解，賠償38萬美元。Bennett指控，Argento在2013年時對他性侵，當時他才17歲，未達法定成年標準。<br />\n<br />\n2004年，7歲的Bennett以童星身分出演電影《心是會騙人的》（The Heart Is Deceitful Above All Things），Argento即為該部電影的導演兼共同編劇。<br />\n<br />\n溫斯坦的律師布拉夫曼表示，溫斯坦得知這項消息時，並未感到太意外：「我不記得原本的措辭，但大意就是鬆了一口氣」。布拉夫曼認為：「這件事發展的偽善程度，超過了震驚一詞所能表達。」<br />\n<br />\n「#MeToo運動」爆發至今，已有超過80名女性指控溫斯坦性騷、性侵和強暴。Argento是其中強有力的發聲代表之一。她也是知名美食節目主持人安東尼波登（Anthony Bourdain）交往多年的女友。"},{"pid":"55ff3d75b60f2805ac27cd41dad8c884f6c74167","tid":791391,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T18:04:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180823/58596492\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180823%2F58596492&d=wCS1pVCWk9FORZ9yatMrf4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=ec1e722f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180823%2F58596492&h=9d178c41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180823/58596492</a>"},{"pid":"cb3b1ab53624ba5f2809ca837ba99762905c7415","tid":791391,"uid":155067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T18:07:53.000Z","msg":"口裡說不"},{"pid":"8aed139bfff60708afb2ebca5dac9d9f585579c1","tid":791391,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T00:17:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b27722c9a6c01324e4753811c58243ca192de6","tid":791391,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T00:46:32.000Z","msg":"咁咪叫男女平等囉<br />\n<br />\n你睇下外國做得幾好"},{"pid":"e3fa33774f855aa61a4549efbc83f4fc6b4bd9ed","tid":791391,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T00:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea726a1cf0a2ccd0f90812e487dc9014980e3b4","tid":791391,"uid":34410,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T01:01:12.000Z","msg":"毒果d女權撚失哂蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"887ccd2cb6baee51d388e24ca01bb7a9cdf891d8","tid":791391,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T01:02:35.000Z","msg":"左膠不意外<br />\n人類毒廇"},{"pid":"d61078606124ea0e9933869f0b6bc0ecd3099859","tid":791391,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T01:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ee9f7e7292b9cd97c47ebf7498aa5d76b1cdda","tid":791391,"uid":199145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T01:41:33.000Z","msg":"啊製片心諗：你條仆街都有今日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asse